%e7%b0%a1%2c1944%2c20211230%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,交簡,1944,20211230,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"1944","JDATE":"20211230","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}